description: My oh my! The food from Mai’s Noodles Express sure is deliciously divine. At this big orange truck, you’ll find a great selection of delectable Asian items: Fried Rice, Teriyaki Chicken, Egg Rolls, Stuffed Chicken Wings, and more... and the Stir Fried Yakisoba Noodles are most prized among Mai’s fans. Kansas City crowds, if you wish to be impressed by your next meal, be sure to visit Mai’s Noodle Express for the best Asian comfort food on wheels.
name: Mai's Noodle Express
